The paper discusses the sensitivity of attribution methods, which are commonly used in machine learning and computer vision. Therefore, the most likely sub-categories are cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.CL (Computation and Language), and cs.CR (Cryptography and Security).
